    {
      "content": "Anybody with a GitHub account can contribute to Azure technical content through our public repository at <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>https://github.com/Azure/azure-content<ept id=\"p1\">](https://github.com/Azure/azure-content)</ept>.",
