    {
      "content": "Install Git for Windows from <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>http://git-scm.com/download/win<ept id=\"p1\">](http://git-scm.com/download/win)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        5101,
        5197
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This download installs the Git version control system, and it installs Git Bash, the command-line app that you will use to interact with your local Git repository.",
      "pos": [
        5198,
        5361
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can accept the default settings; if you want the commands to be available within the Windows command line, select the option that enables it.",
      "pos": [
        5363,
        5508
      ]
    },
    {
